data.title: Queen Celestine
data.text:
Miss Nigeria 2013

Queen participated in the Miss Nigeria 2013 pageant and was the First runner-up.[2]

Most Beautiful Girl in Nigeria (MGBN) 2014

Queen won Miss Amity and was crowned as the MGBN Universe (Most Beautiful Girl in Nigeria) 2014 on July 19, 2014. At same event she was crowned together with the first winner who was crowned as MGBN World 2014, Iheoma Nnadi.[3]
